Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:16.51,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}久留米 九州
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.85,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这次走得真远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:24.40,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}没想到暑假能这样和小泉同学一起旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:27.11,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}只是你擅自跟来的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.82,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}顺着一股劲就从东京跟到了千叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:35.24,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}再北上到青森 沿着日本海沿岸现在到了九州
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:37.62,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不快吃掉该冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.63,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小泉同学 接下来去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.88,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不会就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.51,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.39,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}明天起就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.86,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不管是准备升学还是不准备升学的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:30.06,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:34.40,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}希望各位都有各自的目标 过一个有意义的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.28,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:37.57,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}起立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.12,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.50,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}解放感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.38,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}去哪玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}有意义的暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.09,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}总之去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:55.88,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.34,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}冲绳？台湾？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.84,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}巴厘岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.47,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不要太棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.76,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}旅费昨办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.26,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.47,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.77,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我要上补习班 陪不了你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.52,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}友谊和升学哪个更重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.48,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}升学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.02,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.40,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.28,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}暑假准备怎么过？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:23.12,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}和我们一起去旅行吧 好吗好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.54,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}喂 悠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:25.66,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.58,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}去冲绳啊台湾啊巴厘岛之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:32.42,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}一起吃罕见的拉面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.00,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}总之 明天去哪玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:41.01,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我拒绝 明天我要去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:42.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}日本全国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}全国？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.02,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}喂 我说悠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.70,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:02.95,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.66,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你们两个怎么都这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.49,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不是很准时吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.37,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这种都是要开园前就排队的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.50,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}既然放暑假了 那就鼓足劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.88,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}够拼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.80,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}成人票三张 分开算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.13,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.81,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}最开始果然该从这个开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.23,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.32,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}快 悠 拍照拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.57,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.12,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不错 真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.08,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}感觉美沙还是很享受嘛 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.50,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.84,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}为什么暑假第一天要跑浅草去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.17,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我更情愿去乐园或者海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:04.30,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}抱歉 我傍晚还有补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.10,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我是刚好轮到我做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.27,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}所以就去最近的游乐园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.52,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}预算也比较合适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}接下来去玩那个吧 那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.44,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}向鬼屋出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.65,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.11,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}多大了还去鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.20,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这种人造的怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.04,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}还挺真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.67,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.09,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}刚才好像听到一声挺可爱的惨叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.38,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.18,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}下一个去那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.26,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.60,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}先休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.81,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}啊 好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.89,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}结果你还不是玩得挺开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.02,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.69,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.61,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}有什么活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.74,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.83,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}出租的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.04,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.00,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.50,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}选哪件好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.85,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}挺合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.47,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.10,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}哇 好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.27,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}毕竟是暑假的第一天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:43.32,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}美沙最喜欢热闹了 超兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我倒是不太喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:45.78,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.40,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}怎么了吗 悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.70,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}刚才好像看到小泉同学在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.28,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你是不是越来越不正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.04,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好了 快拍快拍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.02,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}有了 蜜瓜包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.77,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好多人排队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.52,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}哇 好像好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:34.74,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}稍微休息会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:35.49,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.37,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.75,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.46,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}看着就觉得很凉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.42,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.72,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}对了 暑假作业不是要写报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:55.10,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}啊 关于自己的将来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.27,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}咦 有这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.10,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你连看都没看过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.44,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你们打算怎么写？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.27,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}有没有什么将来想做的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.28,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}将来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:12.70,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}会是什么呢 还没认真考虑过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.99,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}连升不升学都没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.54,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}美沙不打算升学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.37,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}因为如果成为了偶像或者模特的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.21,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}哪有时间上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.34,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.80,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}说起来 润你升学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.05,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}准备去什么系的大学？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:34.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那个 其实我还没决定好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:38.77,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这个随便想一个不就好了 反正离考试时间还长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:44.44,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真羡慕你们在这种时期还能这么随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:47.15,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}感觉有点在diss我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.23,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}话说悠你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:54.03,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我的话 应该是从事和拉面有关的职业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.66,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你？不是小泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.87,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}当然是和小泉一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.46,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}和小泉一起你还能干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.25,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:09.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}没错 让喜欢吃拉面的小泉同学红遍大江南北
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.72,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}杂志 影视 还有演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.26,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}认真问你这问题的美沙真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.56,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}别人看着呢 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.23,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}午饭吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.98,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}都怪悠老是说小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.61,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}除了拉面都想不到其他东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.24,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.95,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.63,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}酷暑的天气吃热腾腾的拉面也别有一番风味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.09,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}之前不是还说不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:10:00.18,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不过这种中华荞麦的味道确实让人很想偶尔来一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.23,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我点的梅盐拉面也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.94,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.56,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:12.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}下次叫上小泉同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.86,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}说不定现在就在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:17.91,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}怎么可能 她都说了今天要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.37,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}感觉还是玩得挺开心的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.33,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}都是美沙带你们玩起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.25,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.87,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那我差不多该走了 接下来要去补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.83,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}美沙从这边回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.63,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是吗 那我从这边回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.51,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:34.26,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.63,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.05,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好想再来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.89,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}可以的话下次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.98,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}和小泉同学一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.73,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}快看 小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.65,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}用这双筷子吃拉面不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.53,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.70,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}悠同学 这些看上去很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:58.99,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.91,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真漂亮 就像星空铺了在地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:06.41,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小泉同学真浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:14.05,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好 暑假期间再叫小泉同学来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.34,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.84,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小…小泉同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.39,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.39,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.60,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你不是说今天是去旅行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.93,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是 所以就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.65,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}等等 你看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那里的酱油拉面非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.11,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你知道那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.03,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.11,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}在浅草也有拉面店 很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.24,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}很少见？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.20,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.45,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这浅草可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:52.54,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}所有的 起源之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.30,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}起源之地？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.51,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}对了 你的行李箱里裝了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}作为伴手礼的拉面 拉面Walker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.89,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}还有就是饿肚子时吃的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.60,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我想变成拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:11.44,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}啦啦啦 喜欢拉面的小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.78,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}浅草竟然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.44,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}所有的起源之地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.32,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}虽然有各种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.62,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}但在明治时期 距今一百多年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:30.00,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}在浅草创立的面向百姓的中国料理店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}来来轩所供应的酱油味拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:39.17,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}拉面上有叉烧和麻竹笋 被视为是日本拉面的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.42,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}一百多年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:47.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这家店的主人是土生土长的浅草人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.77,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}在拉面的发祥地浅草追本溯源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.10,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}长年以来一直做着怀旧风味的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.61,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}难怪有一股怀旧的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.40,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}话说回来 还是第一次看到小泉同学穿便服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.99,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.95,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}话说 你要到哪里旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:08.95,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.25,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我现在就在旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:17.04,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小泉同学 也带上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.84,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}挺雅致的一家店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.01,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.84,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.35,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}很简单的拉面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.68,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这里用的是九十九里产的高级煮干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.85,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}一碗使用约40克左右并弄成粉末使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.56,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}将鲜味浓缩出来是这里的特色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.90,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这也是酱油拉面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.28,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.49,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}美味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.59,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}看起来简单 但是回味无穷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.34,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.51,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}下一家是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.72,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}青森拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.56,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这里也用煮干呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.31,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.98,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}看上去好好吃 酱油和汤底好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:20.02,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}发祥自荞麦面的青森拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.53,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}特点是不使用任何油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:25.24,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真的 一点浮油都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:37.62,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}确实是很清爽的味道 能感觉到煮干的风味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.35,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.81,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}咦 这不是刚才那家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:02.40,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我刚才和美沙还有润 三个人在这里吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.82,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那你就不必再来这排队了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.99,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}和小泉同学一起吃的拉面就是另一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.24,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这是什么 汤很黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.58,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}刚才来的时候还没这个拉面的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.62,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是晚间限定的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.79,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}限定？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.55,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}北陆富山的当地拉面 富山黑汤拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.76,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}而这家店加入了自己的创新过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.48,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我也开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.98,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}味道好浓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:48.57,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}胡椒和柚子的搭配真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.79,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}刚才是青森 这回又到了富山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.21,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}感觉就像是旅行一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.71,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}所以我早就说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:05.55,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}诞生在东京平民街区的酱油拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:08.51,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}发展出不同的态 流传至全国各地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.34,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}仅仅是在这浅草转一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:14.72,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}就可以尝遍日本全国的各种拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:21.14,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我正在进行品尝各地拉面的美食之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:25.48,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这样啊 小泉同学真的在旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.11,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我不是一开始就这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:32.99,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}是吗 我是在和小泉同学一起旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.66,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那么 我还要前往旅程的下一站…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.79,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}等等我 都到这里了就让我陪你到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.00,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.50,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:45.96,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:48.30,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.17,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}哇 是豚骨拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.26,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:03.85,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.90,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}虽然都叫做博多拉面 但也各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:12.49,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这家店继承了豚骨拉面发祥之地久留米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.82,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}醇厚汤底 笔直细面的特色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.70,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}久留果 九州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.87,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这次走得真远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:30.25,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}然后这里是继承了佐贺名店 精养轩的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}传说中的佐贺拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.64,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}耗费数月制成的浓厚豚骨汤和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.97,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}饱满柔软的面条是这里的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.85,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.64,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}面稍微粗一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:51.23,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}面条很饱满 豚骨拉面也有各种特色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.07,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.70,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}今天这里是最后一家店了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.74,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不用勉强陪我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.50,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}都到这一步了可没有回头路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.54,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}酱油豚骨拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.17,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}平民区备受欢迎的江户人拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.59,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}这是以浅草为中心向各地扩散的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.68,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}感觉很浓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.14,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.64,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}从浅草开始传扬的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:28.69,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}在九州发展为豚骨拉面 然后又像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.78,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}回到了东京
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.88,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}吃了一整个夏天份的拉面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.42,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}所以我不是提醒过你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.59,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}嗯 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:01.68,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不知为何 突然想起第一次和小泉同学一起吃拉面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.89,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那一次我也吃撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.19,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那是什么时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.94,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:10.65,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.52,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}切 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.61,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}虽然不是真正的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.91,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我们也可以像这样一起品尝各地拉面来旅游啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.58,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我说 下次我门来一次真正的旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.74,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}冲绳怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:27.12,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我想看看小泉同学穿泳装的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:27.96,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.29,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.13,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:33.96,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.80,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}烟花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.74,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}快看啊 小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.96,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}下周有烟花大会 我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.00,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.13,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}去吧去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.42,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我很想看小泉同学穿浴衣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:16.42,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.42,RDKS-MAIN,,700,0,0,,{\blur1}想看想看想看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.32,RDKS-MAIN,,0,700,0,,{\blur1}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.09,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}拜托了 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:22.05,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.85,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}为什么你偷懶没做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.27,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我去周游全国…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:16.17,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}前段时间我和小泉同学去周游全国了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.00,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}旅途中的小泉同学真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.92,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好好 你的梦话我已经听够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.63,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}比起那个 下次我们去海边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:25.22,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}好啊 去吧 也叫上小泉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:28.43,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}小泉同学的泳装 小泉同学的泳装…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:30.05,RDKS-MAIN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我想她绝对不会来
